				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The problem with moving messages into another window is that you do so to lose spam.  Creating another window entirely for spam defeats that purpose, you are moving the problem and not eliminating it.
<br />

<br />
If you downsize the spam window, this helps but if you have lots and lots of messages going there then need to view them after a while (verify enrage was used for example)...my entire screen can freeze for up to 15 seconds while it displays the horde of spam.  This poses a serious problem that results in me not using this method at all.
<br />

<br />
Requesting that specific filters be created is not a huge undertaking - it would be appreciated by all pet classes and probably warriors as well.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=501504">Anthe Battlecaster</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
